commit.message: Add links to slides and code.
Add decorators and context managers presentations.
Revive old PyYYC website. Following Feb 19 2015 presentations by vinc456 and kvoroneau on the new old PyYYC website and HackRun websockets
Added a message for lack of upcoming events
Added extra information to the meetup events; decreased transparency of the site background
Added files to parse data from the meetup api and render it using templates to the events page
Fixed git add caused by the deploy script
Added bower and corresponding files; added requirejs; added background sexiness
